\v 22 ‘\w Obey|strong="H6213"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w my|strong="H8104"\w* laws/decrees [DOU] \w carefully|strong="H6213"\w*, \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w order|strong="H4941"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w you|strong="H3605"\w* \w will|strong="H3808"\w* \w not|strong="H3808"\w* \w be|strong="H3808"\w* forced \w to|strong="H6213"\w* leave [MET] \w the|strong="H3605"\w* land \w to|strong="H6213"\w* \w which|strong="H8033"\w* \w I|strong="H3808"\w* am bringing \w you|strong="H3605"\w*.
